            "term": "Infinitive verb",
            "definition": "The base form of a verb (ends in -ar, -er, -ir), e.g., hablar, comer, vivir."
          },
          {
            "cardId": "f-004",
            "term": "Present tense purpose",
            "definition": "Used to describe actions happening now or habitual actions."
